description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for Band 5 mental Health Nurses to join our inpatient teams at the Derwent Centre.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a newly refurbished Unit, offering 2 adult mental health assessment and treatment wards. this is an opportunity for the successful candidate to develop a number off skills to ensure we support our service users in their recovery pathway.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season Ticket Loans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS discounts for staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Training facilities and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work bank shifts and expand knowledge and experience in other areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary Sacrifice schemes including lease cars and Cycle to Work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buying and Selling annual leave scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01279 637135/164&lt;/p&gt;
